title: 11/24/20 DPS-BEST OF

description:
On Today'e episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Bucs/Rams Game. How concerned should Buccaneers fans be? Was Brady wrong for snubbing Jared Goff post game? We're joined by Bengals Color Analyst Dave Lapham, Michigan State Head Basketball Coach Tom Izzo, Actor Josh Duhamel and Florida Gators QB Kyle Trask.
